hey are known at the time of re-scoring. Intrinsic information has been largely overlooked by language modeling research. The results of both experiments on cgn data and wsj data show that integrating sentence length and word length can achieve improvement. rnnlms allow these features to be incorporated with ease, and obtain improved performance.},
